搵前度傾心事，傾傾下就又做愛，個前度問佢可唔可以內射，台妹搖頭說不，但最後還是被射滿滿，所以話，呢個地方真係十分淫亂。"},{"pid":"6a395085468b3d62ee769fc9feb01b0eaeb1c4da","tid":2375281,"uid":4646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5155662920a5a995a4361d146c7cd486fdfeab1a","tid":2375281,"uid":34577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T02:32:57.000Z","msg":"主動要求畀人搞自己，但係又告人哋強姦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T02:48:21.000Z","msg":"上訴後高雄高分院認為少女是自行喝醉並非被灌醉，改依乘機性交罪改判莊男3年8月徒刑。可上訴。<br />\n<br />\n做男人就係原罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07bdf60f9d7f34c88808bf26761fce68c745430d","tid":2375281,"uid":34577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a395085468b3d62ee769fc9feb01b0eaeb1c4da","tid":2375281,"uid":4646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5155662920a5a995a4361d146c7cd486fdfeab1a","tid":2375281,"uid":34577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T02:32:57.000Z","msg":"主動要求畀人搞自己，但係又告人哋強姦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T02:48:21.000Z","msg":"上訴後高雄高分院認為少女是自行喝醉並非被灌醉，改依乘機性交罪改判莊男3年8月徒刑。可上訴。<br />\n<br />\n做男人就係原罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T02:49:40.000Z","msg":"配合個女仔都叫乘機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e7d8d8e11642a297535e88b1b541231e6e2c5e8","tid":2375281,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T02:54:33.000Z","msg":"個男既都幾慘"},{"pid":"d5ec3ae4d5b9898c84c0fab9e1814c02f2082406","tid":2375281,"uid":158931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T02:57:02.000Z","msg":"乘機性交罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gi